list.title: Iter8or#map
list.description: Applies a function to all elements of the iterator and returns a new Iter8or instance.

list.title: Iter8or#partition
list.description: Partitions the elements of the iterator into two groups based on the predicate function.

list.title: Iter8or#toArray
list.description: Collects the elements of the iterator into an array.

list.title: Iter8or#toMap
list.description:
Collects the elements of the iterator into a Map.
The elements must be pairs [key, value].

list.title: Iter8or#toObject
list.description:
Collects the elements of the iterator into an object.
The elements must be pairs [key, value].

list.title: Iter8or#toSet
list.description: Collects the elements of the iterator into a Set.

list.title: Iter8or#toString
list.description: Concatenates the elements of the iterator into a string.
